              "originalPosition": 318,
              "body": "Does there need to be (or ought there to be) an offset field for the derived field? The checksum and static template fields have offsets, and it feels like it would be easier to know for sure where the various fields go if there is an offset?\n\nI guess if one knows how the packet should be laid out, it will be possible to always know, but maybe that should be spelled out in the registry then?",
